      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with some life left in it? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic wheels, a handy backup car, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s priced with its condition in mind and could be a great fit for the right buyer who appreciates a good value. If you want something inexpensive and approachable without any fluff, this is worth a look.",
