    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with strong fundamentals and plenty of upside for the next owner. It starts, runs, and drives, with an engine that pulls cleanly and a drivetrain that feels serviceable for daily use or a light project build. Cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the ask. Good candidate for someone who wants dependable transportation, a weekend tinkering platform, or an affordable entry point into ownership without paying premium-market money. Priced to move and worth a look if you appreciate honest mechanical potential.",
